<div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333;">
  <div style="background-color: #16a34a; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;">
    <h1 style="color: #ffffff; margin: 0; font-size: 24px;"><%= @trip.name %></h1>
    <p style="color: #dcfce7; margin: 5px 0 0;">Payment Request</p>
  </div>

  <div style="padding: 24px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-top: none; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;">
    <p>Hey <%= @user.first_name %>,</p>

    <p>We're just one week out and it's almost go time! Get ready for some competitive golf, great company, and Scottsdale sunshine. This one's going to be a blast.</p>

    <% if @room_balance > 0 %>
      <p>Here's your remaining balance for the trip:</p>

      <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 20px 0;">
        <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
          <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: #6b7280;">Room (<%= @room_name %>)</td>
          <td style="padding: 10px 0; text-align: right;"><%= number_to_currency(@room_cost) %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
          <td style="padding: 10px 0; color: #6b7280;">Deposit paid</td>
          <td style="padding: 10px 0; text-align: right; color: #16a34a;">-<%= number_to_currency(@deposit_credit) %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 12px 0; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px;">Balance Due</td>
          <td style="padding: 12px 0; text-align: right; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; color: #dc2626;"><%= number_to_currency(@room_balance) %></td>
        </tr>
      </table>

      <p>Send payment via Venmo:</p>
      <p style="text-align: center; margin: 16px 0;">
        <a href="https://venmo.com/drobsokc" style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #008CFF; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: bold;">Pay via Venmo - @drobsokc</a>
      </p>
    <% else %>
      <p>Your room balance is <strong style="color: #16a34a;">paid in full</strong>. You're all set!</p>
    <% end %>

    <div style="margin: 24px 0; padding: 16px; background-color: #fefce8; border: 1px solid #fde68a; border-radius: 8px;">
      <p style="margin: 0 0 8px; font-weight: bold;">Cash Games - Bring $500 Cash</p>
      <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
        <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #fde68a;">
          <td style="padding: 6px 0; color: #6b7280;">Team Bet</td>
          <td style="padding: 6px 0; text-align: right;">$300</td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #fde68a;">
          <td style="padding: 6px 0; color: #6b7280;">Skins</td>
          <td style="padding: 6px 0; text-align: right;">$150</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 6px 0; color: #6b7280;">2's</td>
          <td style="padding: 6px 0; text-align: right;">$50</td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </div>

    <p>Thanks,<br>Duggan</p>
  </div>
</div>
